1.Given an array arr[], the task is to find whether the arr is palindrome or not. If the arr is palindrome then return true else return false.
Platform : GeeksForGeeks
SOURCECODE : class Solution {
    public static boolean isPalindrome(int[] arr) {
     
        int left=0;
        int right=arr.length-1;
        while(left<=right){
            if(arr[left]!=arr[right]){
                return false;
            }
            left++;
            right--;
        }
        return true;
    }
}
